N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 132.5 - Winners list

State Regulations

The rules of the contest shall set forth the address where
persons may obtain a copy of the winners list from the promoter in accordance
with General Business Law, section 369-e(5). Notes
